rows.label: qev092803_SEL0030
rows.name:
Ask if she has any idea where
Alicia might have gone.

rows.label: qev092803_MSG0040
rows.name:
I don't know...
It's rare for her to go outside in the first place...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092803_SEL0070
rows.name: Suggest splitting into two teams to search.

rows.label: qev092803_MSG0090
rows.name: I didn't want to have to resort to this, but...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092803_MSG0100
rows.name:
Leesh's comm device.
It has a tracker installed for such an event.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092803_MSG0110
rows.name:
I may be the pilot, but it's also my job to
ensure the chief engineer's safety.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092803_MSG0125
rows.name: Could she be aboard a Skell?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092803_MSG0130
rows.name: It looks like she's headed for...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092803_MSG0160
rows.name:
Let's move. Dammit...
I've got a bad feeling.[ST:wait ]
